## Attachments [/attachments]

### attachments.list [GET /attachments.list]

Get a list of all attachments relating to an object

+ Request (application/json;charset=utf-8)

    + Attributes (object)
        + page (Page, optional)
        + subject (object, required)
            + type (enum[string], required)
                + contact
                + company
                + deal
                + ticket
                + project
                + event
            + id (string, required)

+ Response 200 (application/json;charset=utf-8)

    + Attributes (object)
        + data (array)
            + (object)
                + id: `101` (number)
                + subject (object)
                    + type (enum[string])
                        + contact
                        + company
                        + deal
                        + ticket
                        + project
                        + event
                    + id (string)
                + name: `logo.eps` (string)
                + size: `256` (number) - in bytes
                + mime_type (string)
                + added_by (object)
                    + type: `user` (enum[string])
                        + Members
                            + user
                    + id (string)
                + added_at: `2017-10-13T00:02:17+0200` (string)
                + updated_at: `2017-10-13T00:02:17+0200` (string)

